<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style type="text/css">
      a, p {
        font-family: Avenir, sans-serif;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      a {
        color: #000cac;
        text-decoration:none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
  <div style="background-color:#fbfbfb">
    <div style="border-bottom:2px solid #eeeeee;background-color:#ffffff">
      <table cellspacing="0" align="center" width="600" cellpadding="0"><tbody>
        <tr>
          <td valign="middle" width="40" height="50">
            <%= link_to root_path, :target => "_blank" do %>
              <%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url, size: "114x32" %>
            <% end %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody></table>
    </div>

    <table align="center" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody>
      <tr><td height="30">&nbsp;</td></tr>
      <tr>
        <td valign="top">
          <%= image_tag attachments['header.jpg'].url, :class => "header" %>
          <table style="border:1px solid #eee;" bgcolor="#ffffff" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="600"><tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="550"><tbody>
                  <tr><td valign="top" colspan="2" height="20">&nbsp;</td></tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="30">&nbsp;</td>
                    <td valign="top" colspan="2" style="text-align:center;">

<p style="font-size:18px;"><strong><%= @sender.full_name %></strong> wants you to join Tipster!</p>

<p>Tipster is the quickest and easiest way to share great content with your friends. Use it to send the page you're currently viewing and they'll receive it directly into their browser - no more copying and pasting URLs!</p>

<p style="margin: 20px 0 25px;">
  <a href="http://www.tipster.to/users/sign_up" style="border:none;padding:10px 50px;margin:15px 0 5px;color:white;background-color:#ff6600;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;border-radius:4px;" target="_blank">
    Sign Up Now
  </a>
</p>

<p>With Tipster you can find out which of your shares are most popular, who was the first of your friends to discover something, and what the people you know are sharing.</p>

<p>We're building a community around great content, making sharing and discovering fun again.</p>

<p><a href="www.tipster.to" target="_blank" %>Click here</a> to find out more, or <a href="www.tipster.to/users/sign_up" target="_blank" %>sign up now</a>.</p>


                    </td>
                    <td width="30">&nbsp;</td>
                  </tr>
       
                  <tr>
                    <td valign="top" height="30" style="height:30px">&nbsp;</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody></table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody></table>
          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" width="540"><tbody>
            <tr>
              <td height="20">&nbsp;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p style="font-size:9pt;color:#8b959e;text-decoration:none;text-align:center">
                  You are receiving this email because your friend wanted to let you know about Tipster.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody></table>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td height="50">&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody></table>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>